WEBVTT

00:01:29.499 --> 00:01:35.142
and forgave the perpetrators,
who voluntarily infected them

00:01:35.166 --> 00:01:37.995
using HIV and rape as a weapon.

00:01:39.937 --> 00:01:42.349
So, they inspired me.

00:01:42.373 --> 00:01:43.929
If they can do that,

00:01:43.953 --> 00:01:46.825
I can stay and try to do my best.

00:01:48.336 --> 00:01:52.415
Those ladies were really activists

00:01:52.439 --> 00:01:55.177
of peace and reconciliation.

00:01:55.201 --> 00:01:58.588
They show us a way
to rebuild a country

00:01:58.612 --> 00:02:02.605
for our children and grandchildren
to have, one day,